                " \nWEST COAST DISTRICT MUNICIPALITY\n ",
                " \nGRADUATE INTERNSHIP FOR 2024 \n \nThe West Coast District Municipality and its B-Municipalities are offering a Graduate Internship Programme for 2024 in the following towns within the West Coast, Western Cape Province: \nBergrivier Municipality \u2013 Piketberg (Ref: BMPB) \nCederberg Municipality \u2013 Clanwilliam (Ref: CMCW) \nMatzikama Municipality \u2013 Vredendal (Ref: MMVD) \nSaldanha Bay Municipality \u2013 Vredenburg (Ref: SBVB) \nSwartland Municipality \u2013 Malmesbury (Ref: SMMLB) \nWest Coast District Municipality \u2013 Moorreesburg (Ref: WCMRB) \n \nThe graduate interns will receive a stipend of R100 000.00 per annum during his/her placement. This programme is aimed at enhancing youth employability and improving service delivery. \n\n \nRequirements: Successfully completed a degree or a national diploma in Human Resource Management or Development at a registered Higher Education institution within the last two years (2022 or 2023); must be a South African citizen and must reside within the abovementioned towns for which the application is. Preferably between the age of 21 \u2013 25. Code B drivers license.",
                "The prescribed application form is available during office hours from Ms C Erasmus on 022-4338421 or on the website at www.westcoastdm.co.za. Completed application form, curriculum vitae and certified copies of documents must be forwarded to West Coast District Municipality, Human Resource Development, 58 Lang Street, Moorreesburg, 7310 or e-mail to tsteinmann@wcdm.co.za.\nIndicate on your application the reference. \n \nClosing Date: 19 January 2024 \n \nShould no feedback from this office be received within 30 days of the closing date, candidates may assume that their applications have been unsuccessful."
